Chansey (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0112: Rhydon
Pokémon
#0114: Tangela →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Chansey (TCG Pocket).

Chansey has been featured on 25 different cards since it debuted in the Base Set of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Chansey cards are normally Colorless-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Chansey

Chansey
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
